{"tid":2242251,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"於682P 發現一隻唔戴口罩嘅熱狗","createTime":"2020-10-14T01:33:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-14T02:09:13.000Z","uid":200849,"like":7,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1238bd6a50bfbb8bf06ddf943de7adc396e828c1","tid":2242251,"uid":200849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T01:33:29.000Z","msg":"車長專登停低部車上黎<br />\n好聲好氣咁勸個男人戴番口罩<br />\n係唔聽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係要被全車人開聲屌先戴番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一路戴 仲要一路拎番個尾彩<br />\n「驚就唔好出街啦！」<br />\n十足十陳雲啲弟子口吻<br />\n擺出一副自命清高 眾人皆醉我獨醒嘅姿態<br />\n仲要係條光頭柒黎 成個黃洋達咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後咪又係急急腳咁衝落車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n熱狗真係毒瘤黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75c7375e6e1b74b6339edc280d01af6c2d09e2dc","tid":2242251,"uid":244521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T01:35:02.000Z","msg":"邊條撚樣嚟&nbsp;好快快脆脆認咗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0c703d6273244bd2fdf300114d17d584b56bdc9","tid":2242251,"uid":309553,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T01:53:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4zN1Ly2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4zN1Ly2.png&h=352a5b59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n國屍都戴喎"},{"pid":"f49dba67fa60e381ae2b55e306d708f30ebf121e","tid":2242251,"uid":200849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75c7375e6e1b74b6339edc280d01af6c2d09e2dc","tid":2242251,"uid":244521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T01:35:02.000Z","msg":"邊條撚樣嚟&nbsp;好快快脆脆認咗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asse